The paper discusses security issues in P2P networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves the study of propagation mechanisms, which can be related to network security (cs.NI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also explores the challenges and evaluates the impact of P2P worms on the network, which can be categorized under social and information networks (cs.SI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
